      <text:p>tts</text:p>
     </table:table-cell>
     <table:table-cell office:value-type="string" calcext:value-type="string">
      <text:p>A</text:p>
     </table:table-cell>
     <table:table-cell office:value-type="string" calcext:value-type="string">
      <text:p>string</text:p>
     </table:table-cell>
     <table:table-cell office:value-type="string" calcext:value-type="string">
      <text:p>texte libre</text:p>
     </table:table-cell>
     <table:table-cell office:value-type="string" calcext:value-type="string">
      <text:p>_</text:p>
     </table:table-cell>
     <table:table-cell office:value-type="string" calcext:value-type="string">
      <text:p>SP→SE</text:p>
     </table:table-cell>
     <table:table-cell office:value-type="string" calcext:value-type="string">
      <text:p>*</text:p>
     </table:table-cell>
     <table:table-cell office:value-type="string" calcext:value-type="string">
      <text:p>_</text:p>
     </table:table-cell>
     <table:table-cell office:value-type="string" calcext:value-type="string">
      <text:p>Dyn</text:p>
     </table:table-cell>
     <table:table-cell office:value-type="string" calcext:value-type="string">
      <text:p>Event</text:p>
     </table:table-cell>
     <table:table-cell office:value-type="string" calcext:value-type="string">
      <text:p>_</text:p>
     </table:table-cell>
     <table:table-cell office:value-type="string" calcext:value-type="string">
      <text:p>$A:Voice:tts:*:&quot;Démarrage terminé&quot;#</text:p>
     </table:table-cell>
     <table:table-cell office:value-type="string" calcext:value-type="string"><text:p>SP demande à SE de prononcer un texte via termux-tts-speak.</text:p><text:p>Géré directement dans rz_vpiv_parser.sh (case A / MODULE=Voice).</text:p><text:p>Les guillemets sont retirés avant envoi au moteur TTS.</text:p>
     </table:table-cell>
    </table:table-row>
