      <text:p>ExprTasker</text:p>
     </table:table-cell>
     <table:table-cell office:value-type="string" calcext:value-type="string">
      <text:p>A</text:p>
     </table:table-cell>
     <table:table-cell office:value-type="string" calcext:value-type="string">
      <text:p>string</text:p>
     </table:table-cell>
     <table:table-cell office:value-type="string" calcext:value-type="string">
      <text:p>voir INSTANCE</text:p>
     </table:table-cell>
     <table:table-cell office:value-type="string" calcext:value-type="string">
      <text:p>_</text:p>
     </table:table-cell>
     <table:table-cell office:value-type="string" calcext:value-type="string">
      <text:p>SP→SE</text:p>
     </table:table-cell>
     <table:table-cell office:value-type="string" calcext:value-type="string">
      <text:p>Expression (nom expression) | Info (texte) | Off (*)</text:p>
     </table:table-cell>
     <table:table-cell office:value-type="string" calcext:value-type="string">
      <text:p>_</text:p>
     </table:table-cell>
     <table:table-cell office:value-type="string" calcext:value-type="string">
      <text:p>Dyn</text:p>
     </table:table-cell>
     <table:table-cell office:value-type="string" calcext:value-type="string">
      <text:p>Event</text:p>
     </table:table-cell>
     <table:table-cell office:value-type="string" calcext:value-type="string">
      <text:p>_</text:p>
     </table:table-cell>
     <table:table-cell office:value-type="string" calcext:value-type="string">
      <text:p>$A:Appli:ExprTasker:Expression:sourire#</text:p>
     </table:table-cell>
     <table:table-cell office:value-type="string" calcext:value-type="string"><text:p>Expression → tâche RZ_Expression (expressions faciales robot).</text:p><text:p>Info → tâche RZ_Info (affichage message sur écran SE).</text:p><text:p>Off → arrêt ExprTasker.</text:p><text:p>⚠️ L&apos;INSTANCE porte le type d&apos;action (≠ autres Appli où INSTANCE=*).</text:p><text:p>La VALUE porte l&apos;argument (nom expression ou texte).</text:p>
     </table:table-cell>
    </table:table-row>
